text: More DK is an EP released by the Danish industrial band Psychopomps. These tracks were later re-released on the EP In The Skin. ==Track listing== ==Personnel== *Jesper Schmidt: Vox, Programming, Keyboards *Flemming Norre Larsen: Programming, Lyrics ==External links== * Psychopomps at myspace Category:1991 EPs Category:Psychopomps (band) albums
